{"tid":776420,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"熱刺捧國冠盃喜上加喜","createTime":"2018-08-12T05:24:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T08:58:45.000Z","uid":2169,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"95a989f42d41f496b8c5ae5cfa6bd87360fc6f13","tid":776420,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T05:24:07.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=MeSrQFrfhZOm9hg6GOhevW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=e8688fae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】為期近1個月的國際冠軍盃落幕，周末在英超打開勝門的熱刺，終力壓群雄得到冠軍，可說雙喜。<br />\n<br />\n由18支歐洲頂級球隊角逐的國際冠軍盃，在周末隨著國際米蘭以1:0小勝馬德里體育會而結束，由於國米贏波幅度小，最終在得失球差方面不及同樣3戰得7分的多蒙特與熱刺，後者成為這個季前賽的冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n熱刺3場比賽分別以4:1勝羅馬、2:2賽和巴塞隆拿後互射12碼敗陣（得1分），然後以1:0小勝AC米蘭。<br />\n<br />\n國冠盃可說是列強操兵場所，熱刺多名主力征戰今夏世界盃，故球隊主要以副選及年青球員出戰，最終贏得一個季前錦標，對2線兵尤其鼓舞。值得一提是包尾球隊為巴塞隆拿，除了互射12碼贏最終冠軍熱刺外，其餘兩戰皆北。<br />\n<br />\n國冠盃最終前列排名<br />\n排名\t球隊\t賽\t勝\tP勝\t負\tP負\t得球\t失球\t積分<br />\n1\t熱刺\t3\t2\t0\t0\t1\t6\t2\t7<br />\n2\t多蒙特\t3\t2\t0\t0\t1\t6\t3\t7<br />\n3\t國際米蘭\t3\t2\t0\t0\t1\t2\t1\t7<br />\n4\t阿仙奴\t3\t1\t1\t0\t1\t7\t3\t6<br />\n5\t利物浦\t3\t2\t0\t1\t0\t7\t5\t6<br />\n<br />\nP勝 = 互射12碼勝，得2分<br />\nP負\t= 互射12碼負，得1分<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"637b22b5ce56bbfb8398277c7936d32064af4694","tid":776420,"uid":36238,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T05:25:42.000Z","msg":"未來已降臨"},{"pid":"b0a82bd187a32da96ac00bfc0528fbfcaad320c3","tid":776420,"uid":69213,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T05:25:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb284a77336e32dad6173a4e23f369d9ce6aebc3","tid":776420,"uid":164730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T05:40:18.000Z","msg":"巴塞包尾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cafc5abe3429dab9fe7188e485c8b0cf94e6672","tid":776420,"uid":58811,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T06:35:10.000Z","msg":"係唔係未來熱第一次冠軍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dfdf191077e0553a226c3b96e2d1de308255658","tid":776420,"uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9cafc5abe3429dab9fe7188e485c8b0cf94e6672","tid":776420,"uid":58811,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T06:35:10.000Z","msg":"係唔係未來熱第一次冠軍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T06:41:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.standard.co.uk/s3fs-public/thumbnails/image/2017/05/26/16/tottenham-kitchee-sc-260517x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.standard.co.uk%2Fs3fs-public%2Fthumbnails%2Fimage%2F2017%2F05%2F26%2F16%2Ftottenham-kitchee-sc-260517x.jpg&h=7cb67dbd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1fb15134a408b95ace13f1faeb3de27e4404317d","tid":776420,"uid":27485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T06:46:31.000Z","msg":"有冇捧盃睇"},{"pid":"1c2916e15e2d85b14e83438c9f7a80a734d66328","tid":776420,"uid":2811,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T06:50:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/145013_8c81ce895f5cf2b6bab6d41d6d5a978e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F145013_8c81ce895f5cf2b6bab6d41d6d5a978e.png&h=1b2b792d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有盃放了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de4f72a87084437fe7600f786a2f88d216f31233","tid":776420,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T06:52:03.000Z","msg":"孫興文拎個盃返去免兵役啦"},{"pid":"9dfbf8160daf1a4dc6d3bcd2dabb1cd53cf7a479","tid":776420,"uid":40940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T08:46:28.000Z","msg":"又可以出DVD <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c811354dc57530b1af8210c4f5c3d1367a684d4e","tid":776420,"uid":31,"li